## Description
This project is a Spring Boot backend application that provides a REST API
for managing products.

The application exposes endpoints to retrieve product data in JSON format.
It uses an in-memory H2 database and Spring Data JPA.

## Technologies
- Java 23
- Spring Boot
- Spring Web
- Spring Data JPA
- H2 Database
- Maven

## How to Run
1. Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA
2. Run the `BackendApplication` class
3. The server will start on port 8080

## API Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

Returns a list of products in JSON format.

## Database
H2 in-memory database
H2 Console: http://localhost:8080/h2-console
